summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1, 2, 29 and 30, in Blocks 1, 2 and 3, Highland View Addition together with vacated streets adjoining located south of vacated West 90th St., between vacated 20th Ave. N.W. and 17th Ave. N.W., with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto one new section numbered 2-440.
